title: Music Therapy [Virtual]
description: Music therapy is for everyone! Join WC Partners and the Center for Music Therapy and Wellness for this virtual music therapy session. Classes are once per week. Contact your Support Coordinator to sign-up.

title: Making Strides Walking Club
description: Join Jennifer and our New Friends with Making Strides walking club! Beginning April 1st (Thursday) we will meet at the Rotary Park at 11:00 am to 11:30 am for walking and socializing. The club will meet each Tuesday and Thursday for 6 weeks (April 1st to May 11th). Prizes for individuals that attend all 12 sessions.

title: Goal Getters
description: This is a support group that will meet beginning April 1st to May 6th from 3:30 pm to 4:30 pm. (if you work at the Workshop we will see if the bus can drop you off) This group will be limited in size, but do not let that stop you from signing up. Each week there will be a healthy food option to try. There will be prizes at the end of the 6 weeks.
